/etc/csf/csf.conf :

add:
RESTRICT_SYSLOG = "3"   ## 2021-05-13 change "0" to "3" in order to avoid this error message:
                    ##  *WARNING* RESTRICT_SYSLOG is disabled. See SECURITY WARNING in /etc/csf/csf.conf
                    
/etc/csf/csf.conf    ##  https://globedrill.com/warning-testing-mode-is-enabled-not-forget-disable-configuration/

##  Change the line TESTING = “1” to TESTING = “0”    ## 2021-06-25

also manually restart ldf.service if the "failed" indicator comes on in the webmin website console.

and be sure to check:
/var/lib/csf/csf.tempban
/var/lib/csf/csf.tempallow

